{"tid":524112,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一圖睇晒！鄭若驊夫婦兩幢獨立屋涉9處僭建","createTime":"2018-01-09T09:04:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-10T06:05:04.000Z","uid":39464,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"22d448cc3489f7cfd0d51b281b3f7140ce2d8963","tid":524112,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T09:04:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180109/large/1515487339_70bd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180109%2Flarge%2F1515487339_70bd.png&h=e9b5270c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屋宇署派人到新任律政司司長鄭若驊夫婦位於屯門大欖的海詩別墅3號及4兩幢相連的獨立屋調查，發現兩幢屋合共有多達9處僭建，其中鄭持有的4號屋共有4處，其餘5處僭建則位於鄭的丈夫、潘樂陶持有的3號屋。<br />\n<br />\n【鄭若驊4號屋僭建位置】<br />\n1. 天台屋 - 尺寸：3.5米 X 2.5米<br />\n2. 地下外牆擴建物 - 尺守：0.5米 X 5米<br />\n3. 地庫 - 面積：50平方米、高2.5米<br />\n4. 車房對出「L」形玻璃簷篷 - 面積：15平方米<br />\n<br />\n【潘樂陶3號屋僭建位置】<br />\n5. 天台屋 - 尺寸：3.5米 X 2.5米<br />\n6. 地下外牆 - 尺寸：1米 X 5米，高7.5米<br />\n7. 水池 - 尺守：5米 X 2.5米，高1米<br />\n8. 地庫 - 面積：50平方米，高3.5米<br />\n9. 地下車房對出2個玻璃簷篷 - 面積：8平方米及4平方米<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180109/57685826\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180109%2F57685826&d=vByXwq9A9S3qxfAYXRYBf%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=630b779b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180109%2F57685826&h=5d7c43bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180109/57685826</a>"},{"pid":"b41686f2eee2aae4fca4715a15921d598343c6fe","tid":524112,"uid":35814,"like":0,"dislike":16,"score":-16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T09:08:15.000Z","msg":"今次會唔會好似唐英年單野咁要出吊臂影相？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d29857cd70f21e441956a21bf9b3a30daccedb8","tid":524112,"uid":57787,"like":43,"dislike":1,"score"